I would like to describe a nice thing someone did for me last vacation when I was with my family in Istanbul - Turkey, we had did many interesting things and we sit in a amazing hotel near to the beach but when was in the big restaurant happened a nice thing, when I finished I went to the bathroom I then entered to the bathroom the door closed I was inside. I wanted someone to me I sit for about 30 min. Surprisingly person came to opened the door, he was my old best friend he was works in this restaurant I was very happy because I met him after all this years, I hope to come back there and see my friend again.